text: Ibrahima Diallo may refer to: * Ibrahima Diallo (politician) (1915-1958), Senegalese politician * Ibrahima Diallo (judoka) (born 1959), Senegalese judoka * Ibrahima Diallo (footballer, born 1985) (born 1985), retired Guinean footballer * Ibrahima Diallo (Paralympic footballer) (born 1993), English Paralympic footballer for Bitton A.F.C. * Ibrahima Diallo (footballer, born 1999) (born 1999), French footballer for Southampton F.C. * Ibrahima Kandia Diallo (born 1941), Guinean footballer ==See also== * Ibrahim Diallo (born 1996), Malian footballer
title: Ibrahima Diallo
